<figureCitation box="[934,1015,1130,1156]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="7.[136,229,1902,1924]" captionTargetBox="[195,1392,190,1878]" captionTargetId="figure-17@7.[195,1392,190,1878]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 3. Species of Fabaceae Lindl. of the study area, Pico do Jabre State Park, Paraíba, Brazil. a Centrosema brasilianum. b Platymiscium floribundum. c Macropsychanthus grandiflorus d Centrosema sagittatum. e Ancistrotropis peduncularis. f Poecilanthe grandiflora. g Erythrina velutina. h Chamaecrista repens. i Canavalia brasiliensis. j Bauhinia cheilantha. k Stylosanthes viscosa. l Crotalaria vitelina. (Source: the authors)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6875647" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6875647/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Fig. 3k</figureCitation>
